assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Sunmoon Food Company Limited, an investment holding company, distributes and markets branded fresh produce, aquatics, animal proteins, and other food related products worldwide. The company offers apples and pears; stone fruits, such as peaches, donut peaches, and nectarines; and seasonal fruits comprising cherries, red globe grapes, pomegranate, Korean strawberry, longan, and mangosteen. It also provides fruit cups, juices, snacks, and frozen foods; and seafood and meat products.In addition, it is involved in the import, export, and distribution of edible agricultural products, office supplies, costumes, articles of daily use, and hardware and home appliances; provision of business information consulting, freight forwarding, business, and warehousing services; supply chain management; food management; sales of edible agricultural products, gift flowers, arts and crafts, ceremonial supplies, and clothing and accessories; domestic cargo transportation agency; import and export of goods, technology import and export, and e-commerce business. Further, the company offers information consulting, and conference and exhibition services. The company distributes products through supermarkets, convenience stores, online and wholesale channels, airlines, and food services, as well as franchise outlets. The company was formerly known as FHTK Holdings, Ltd and changed its name to Sunmoon Food Company Limited. Sunmoon Food Company Limited was founded in 1965 and is headquartered in Singapore. Sunmoon Food Company Limited is a subsidiary of Yiguo General Food Pte Ltd.
